title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: The more youre able to enjoy yourself alone, the more you can share yourself with the world. The intuitive Pisces Full Moon sails through your 5th House of Creativity, heightening the importance of how you relish your private pleasures. But you might also worry that people will place heavy demands on your downtime. Nevertheless, you are in control of your personal calendar. When you claim space to savor your own company, you are liable to feel rejuvenated enough to link up with others for serious playtime later on. Author Sue Krebs wrote, In reaching for balance we find alignment. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
